                    },
                    "message": "PELs are an IBM only thing so it's better not to put those in the common repos.  Instead, you can show part of openbmc D-bus event log, which you can get from 'obmcutil showlogs' ,and then 'obmcutil listlog'."
                },
                {
                    "file": "/COMMIT_MSG",
